text: Gisèle Jourda s'exprime à la tribune du Sénat Gisèle Jourda (born 24 March 1955) is a member of the French Senate, representing the department of Aude. She was elected to the French senate on 28 September 2014. Jourda is deputy mayor of Trèbes. == References == Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:French Senators of the Fifth Republic Category:Women members of the Senate (France) Category:21st-century French women politicians Category:Senators of Aude
